<br>
My guild brethren are considering having a guild war, or more accurately, a guild battle. You know, the two armies on an open plain kind of deal. This would of course be out of fun and not malice.<br>
<br>
Can a war be ended anytime?<br>
<br>
Any guilds out there that would consider this? Fate's Decree is definitely not uber, and we're just trying to get the info before we decide. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umogglenottewbrite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Moggle Nottewbrite</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=" http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master of Darkness </span><br>  Posts: 388<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(10/4/01 4:50:23 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Guild war anyone?</span><hr size=1> Whats the level range of your guild? <p><b>Gilgurth: and you'll die in what?  2 hits?<br>
