</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F25><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ukronx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kronx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(10/4/01 4:55:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Guild war anyone?</span><hr size=1> We could muster maybe 2 50-55ish groups. Our leader is only 58 I think.<br>
<br>
Maybe two 40+ groups.<br>
<br>
That's with an optimistic estimate, so don't hold me to it. <br>
<br>
