Am I correct in the asumption that guild war deaths don't result in XP loss? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umogglenottewbrite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Moggle Nottewbrite</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=" http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master of Darkness </span><br>  Posts: 389<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(10/4/01 4:56:24 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Guild war anyone?</span><hr size=1> I think your correct<br>
